Package ml.karmaconfigs.lockloginmodules.shared.listeners.events.user

Class UserPreJoinEvent

java.lang.Object
ml.karmaconfigs.lockloginmodules.shared.listeners.events.util.Event
ml.karmaconfigs.lockloginmodules.shared.listeners.events.user.UserPreJoinEvent
public final class UserPreJoinEvent
extends Event
This event is fired when a player joins the server at the eyes of the plugin. In bukkit, this event is fired with AsyncPlayerPreLoginEvent, and with PreLoginEvent in BungeeCord
